M|Novi|tx|\| Cold — Interest \| Fashion, luxury brands, Vogue, lifestyle publications \|
M|Novi|tx|\| Cold — Lookalike \| 1–3% LAL of purchasers \|
M|Novi|tx|\| Warm — Engagers \| IG/FB page engagers (last 60 days) \|
M|Novi|tx|\| Retargeting \| Website visitors (last 30 days), add-to-cart abandoners \|
