M|Ad C|Ever|hl + body (optional) + CTA
M|Ad C|**He|**
M|Ad C|- Be|"[Outcome] w/o [pain point]"
M|Ad C|- Cu|"Why [audience] are switching to [vt]"
M|Ad C|- So|"[Number] people already [outcome]"
M|Ad C|**Bo|** 1–2 sentences max. Expand the hl. Do not repeat it.
M|Ad C|**CT|** One action only. Match to cg objective:
M|Ad C|it|Awareness → "Learn more"
M|Ad C|it|Traffic → "Shop now" / "See how it works"
M|Ad C|it|Conversion → "Start free" / "Get yours"
M|Ad C|tx|ro writes the st brief. ln writes the actual words. ro reviews for conversion fit.
M|Ad C|tx|---
M|Perf|tx|\| Metric \| nz Target \| hb Target \|
M|Perf|tx|\|--------\|---------------\|----------------\|
M|Perf|tx|\| CTR \| > 1.5% \| > 2.0% \|
M|Perf|tx|\| CPM \| < $8 \| < $12 \|
M|Perf|tx|\| ROAS \| > 2.5x \| — \|
M|Perf|tx|\| CAC \| < $15 (first purchase) \| < $8 (app install) \|
M|Perf|| LT|CAC \| > 3:1 \| > 3:1 \|
M|Perf|If a|pause, diagnose, rebuild.
M|Perf|tx|---
M|A/B |Ever|
M|A/B |tx|```
M|A/B |Hypo|[If we change X, then Y will improve bc Z]
M|A/B |Vari|[what is being tested — one change only]
M|A/B |Cont|[current version]
M|A/B |Vari|[new version]
M|A/B |Prim|[the single number that determines winner]
M|A/B |Min |[usually 7–14 days]
M|A/B |Min |[$X per variant — enough for statistical significance]
M|A/B |Succ|[e.g., 20% CTR improvement]
M|A/B |tx|```
M|A/B |tx|tst one variable at a time. Never tst hl + im + audience simultaneously.
M|A/B |tx|---
M|Budg|tx|1. New cg — start w/ minimum viable spend (1–2 weeks at lo budget)
M|Budg|tx|2. Winning creative — scale spend 20–30% every 3 days max to avoid fatigue
M|Budg|tx|3. Never increase budget more than 2x in one change — algorithm resets
M|Budg|tx|4. Kill an ad set after 7 days w/ < 50% of benchmark perf
M|Budg|tx|5. Always reserve 20% of budget for testing; 80% to proven performers
M|Budg|tx|---
M|Attr|tx|yv uses **7-day click, 1-day view** attribution as default.
M|Attr|When|
M|Attr|it|Always specify attribution window
M|Attr|it|Compare to organic baseline (ka's data)
M|Attr|it|Never count a conversion if there's no plausible ad touchpoint
M|Attr|tx|---
M|Paid|it|Audience × Creative × Offer — op the weakest link, not all three at once.
M|Paid|it|tst one variable at a time. Kill underperformers at the 7-day benchmark.
M|Paid|- **|scaling a cg before it has statistically sig data.
M|Ad C|it|Pattern interrupt in first 3 seconds. Problem → agitate → solve structure.
M|Ad C|- St|2–3 weeks. Refresh before fatigue, not after.
M|Ad C|- **|benefit-led ad w/o a hook — nobody reads past line 1.
M|Page|- Ab|hl, subheadline, CTA, and one trust signal.
M|Page|it|Single CTA per page. Competing CTAs reduce conversion.
M|Page|- **|sliders, autoplay vd, and popups on page load.
M|Payw|it|Show value before price. Match upgrade trigger to the "aha moment."
M|Payw|it|Frame as "unlock more" not "upgrade to paid" — the mental md matters.
M|Payw|- **|paywall modals that block us from seeing what they'd get.
M|Onbo|it|First meaningful action within 60 seconds. Progressive disclosure of features.
M|Onbo|it|sc milestone before feature tour — let them win before you explain.
M|Onbo|- **|onboarding flows that frontload cfg before value.